Package kea.exercise.hogwartsstudentadmin.edu.hogwarts.dto

Record Class StudentResponseDTO

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
kea.exercise.hogwartsstudentadmin.edu.hogwarts.dto.StudentResponseDTO
Record Components:
id - The unique identifier for the student.
name - The full name of the student. This is a String that represents the full name of the student.
dateOfBirth - The date of birth of the student. This is a LocalDate object that represents the date of birth of the student.
house - The house of the student. This is a String that represents the house of the student.
isPrefect - The prefect status of the student. This is a Boolean that represents whether the student is a prefect or not.
enrollmentYear - The enrollment year of the student. This is an Integer that represents the enrollment year of the student.
graduationYear - The graduation year of the student. This is an Integer that represents the graduation year of the student.
isGraduated - The graduation status of the student. This is a Boolean that represents whether the student has graduated or not.
schoolYear - The school year of the student. This is an Integer that represents the school year of the student.
public record StudentResponseDTO(Long id, String name, LocalDate dateOfBirth, String house, Boolean isPrefect, Integer enrollmentYear, Integer graduationYear, Boolean isGraduated, Integer schoolYear) extends Record
Data Transfer Object for StudentResponse

This record is used to transfer data related to a student response. It includes information about the student such as the student id, name, date of birth, house, prefect status, enrollment year, graduation year, graduation status, and school year.
